備註 Remarks
     參與教學的業師 Lawrence (Larry) Philbrook
 
學經歷：Certified ICA ToP Facilitator (CToPF) and Assessor. IAF CPF 2007-2011. 2013 -2017. Named to the IAF Hall of Fame. He designs processes for teams and leaders in varied cultural settings for over forty years. Larry joined the ICA in 1972 and worked outside the US since 1977 doing extensive company and community-based projects in over 30 nations including 25 years as director of ICA Taiwan. Larry’s key skill is in tailoring designs and facilitation processes to specific needs while helping to recover a sense of respect and trust as a basis for transformation. 

在ICA組織的支持之下，本課程進行過程中，每組團隊將有一位專業引導師全程參與，協助團隊成員有效學習與營造合作共創的學習情境。




